					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10192206#post-4142130</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10192206/scp-3854#post-4142130</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 05 Feb 2019 04:12:50 +0000</pubDate>
								<wikidot:authorUserId>4504036</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This was a collaboration by my fabulous friend <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3027978&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549342158" alt="mlister" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3027978)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mlister" >mlister</a></span> and me.</p> <p>We had gone through several transitions with the article from a nuclear submarine fish to the theatre to keeping the theatre but cutting out a gore-ridden script to refactoring that script into a more whimsical, modern script in order to buckle down on the anachronistic nature of the construct. Finished and topped off by mlister's end log to help contextualize the sights and purpose of the construct, with copious edits.</p> <p>Thank you to all who have read it!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
